{"tid":1443070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急聯署】正式確認香港警察係恐怖分子","createTime":"2019-08-11T06:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T01:01:14.000Z","uid":268935,"like":65,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"597482cb1047bbd7399a4b8446ddc8f19110b344","tid":1443070,"uid":268935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:25:35.000Z","msg":"仲爭5萬人呀，快撚d簽啦屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization?fbclid=IwAR3w9c3ADJXWzWx5u9iqZpjnuqLj6cGf734LZnrbRJe-6BmCIj1-CxqbqUE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3w9c3ADJXWzWx5u9iqZpjnuqLj6cGf734LZnrbRJe-6BmCIj1-CxqbqUE&d=gk%2Bh3YXCSP8KuySO9FkCKmVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=d58bff5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization?fbclid=IwAR3w9c3ADJXWzWx5u9iqZpjnuqLj6cGf734LZnrbRJe-6BmCIj1-CxqbqUE</a>"},{"pid":"068270930bf56af23faca607dcda1b3fda334911","tid":1443070,"uid":268935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:28:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25ad9c58cb7701ec79911241c4083f842c3bb936","tid":1443070,"uid":41245,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:30:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣核彈 - 為恐怖主義正名</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEh1L51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEh1L51.jpg&h=6b5d83e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恐怖主義標籤係諸國用嚟打壓異己嘅手法，「國家當局可用以將政敵或其他對手非法化，從而使國家武裝部隊可理直氣壯地打擊敵人」，包括支那對新疆嘅打壓，都係以打擊恐怖主義為名，效果顯著。若果我地為警隊嘅恐怖主義正名，絕對係致命打擊警隊嘅合法性同認受性嘅方法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別襲擊製造恐怖氣氛絕對已經係恐怖主義！我地係嘅係要為警隊嘅行為正名！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">警隊失控無差別襲擊，係屬於國家恐怖主義嘅行為，已經超越「過度暴力」、「濫捕」同「濫用暴力」，依啲字眼淡化佢嘅「拐帶」、「恐怖襲擊」等非法行為，警隊嘅行為喺好多國家已經係可以定義為失去合法性啲武裝組織。<br />\n而且加上721恐襲同打後嘅黑警合作，有理由相信依個恐怖主義組織係跨越明同暗。現時警察喺民間嘅認受性極低，成為過街老鼠，執法行動已變質，失去合法地執行職務嘅能力，街坊見到警察嘅武裝會產生恐懼感。恐怖主義管治已引起社會及國際極度不安。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fool1-1.fna&amp;oh=58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026&amp;oe=5DD55B02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fool1-1.fna%26oh%3D58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026%26oe%3D5DD55B02&h=2d15fa1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=gk%2Bh3YXCSP8KuySO9FkCKmVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=0f5cf52f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有<span style=\"color: orange;\">47,835</span>/100,000個簽名（11 Aug 2019 at 14:30）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作 恐怖治國<br />\n警察本色 恐怖組織</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">槍炮化武 無差別襲擊<br />\n警黑勾結 武裝巴結<br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n821守衛香港 反警黑恐怖治國 反恐大遊行/集會（未定）<br />\n821 - 元朗恐襲紀念日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442294</a>"},{"pid":"d530bc12c312f1626ca9225939790014b9fcd0bc","tid":1443070,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:32:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c3e5f67e7202c566af242fc353f6675055d2eb8","tid":1443070,"uid":209700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:36:28.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"52b88b9a6dd97c61f4e1e6237a0bd161763359e3","tid":1443070,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:37:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6aa257f4823bd62f21136793bed3a62ab9a13e8","tid":1443070,"uid":196604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"597482cb1047bbd7399a4b8446ddc8f19110b344","tid":1443070,"uid":268935,"like":0,"di